Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.01,0:04:55.85,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,淨是去海外旅遊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:04:59.21,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 這個動畫人物當頭像的是會計
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.22,0:05:00.22,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我對他沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.58,0:05:04.20,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 先到處亂點習慣一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.59,0:05:05.50,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.75,0:05:08.23,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我就先回去泡澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.03,0:05:18.46,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這工作真是累死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:22.67,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要是不像這樣泡澡輕鬆一下根本干不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:26.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,輝夜大小姐根本不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.68,0:05:29.73,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要多珍惜我一點啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.31,0:05:32.03,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,早坂 趕緊過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.26,0:05:35.97,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,輝夜大小姐 別這樣突然進來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:38.12,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我的推特被拉黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:40.88,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真虧你知道拉進黑名單這詞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:43.28,Kaguya_zw,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&HEAE9EB&\bord0\3c&HF5F4F6&\1a&H00&\an7\pos(315.2,366.4)}m 0 0 l 0 700 l 1000 700 l 1000 0
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:43.28,Kaguya_hm_heiti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\c&H9C9EA0&\fs85\pos(344,512)}推送設置為不公開。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:43.28,Kaguya_hm_heiti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\c&H9C9EA0&\fs85\pos(344,371.2)}本賬號的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:43.28,Kaguya_hm_heiti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\c&H9C9EA0&\fs65\pos(385,819.2)}經白銀御行先生許可的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:43.28,Kaguya_hm_heiti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\c&H9C9EA0&\fs65\pos(385,889.6)}才能查看個人資料。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.51,0:05:46.68,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 看不到啊 我做了什麼壞事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:49.71,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,白銀會長的賬號是私密賬號啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.04,0:05:50.97,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,私密賬號？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.32,0:05:54.35,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,因為有一發生什麼事就高潮的鍵盤俠在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.89,0:05:57.97,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,會長在信息安全方面的意識非常強
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:06:00.71,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我的主賬號也是設成私密賬號的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:03.04,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,輝夜大小姐也要多多注意…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:06.55,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說 請把賬號當成自家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:12.52,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,普通賬號就像是開放玄關隨人進
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.92,0:06:15.99,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 為了防止居心叵測的人就得給家門上個鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:19.15,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,只給限定的幾個可以看的人鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.18,0:06:23.53,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 那要去哪裡獲得那個鑰匙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:27.27,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,很簡單啊 只要點一下這個「關注」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.59,0:06:31.13,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就能給白銀會長遞交許可申請了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.40,0:06:34.65,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,只要他通過了 你就能看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.00,0:06:38.78,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,在個人資料裡說明是秀知院學生 大概都會通過的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:41.63,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這 這種事…這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.32,0:06:44.12,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼做得到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:46.56,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,因為 那不就意味著…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.50,0:06:51.74,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,會長 快開門
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.77,0:06:54.32,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我想了解會長的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.48,0:06:59.03,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,想知道你平時都想什麼 都在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:58.35,Kaguya_hm_songti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\c&H020202&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fad(1000,1000)}等待許可中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.80,0:07:03.13,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你就這麼想了解我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.35,0:07:07.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然對我僅有140字的自言自語如此有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.17,0:07:12.89,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可愛的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.86,0:07:14.95,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.02,0:07:16.73,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你是笨蛋新手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.73,0:07:20.63,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真的一天到晚想些有的沒的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:22.57,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 早坂你生氣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.76,0:07:24.35,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,比起說生沒生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:27.01,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你想讓我半裸到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:28.79,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.85,0:07:30.11,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要是輝夜大小姐你不動手的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.12,0:07:32.49,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 等等等等 等等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.65,0:07:34.63,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我會按自己的節奏去做的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:51.85,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,會長他究竟都會發推說些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:55.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,平時都在做什麼 喜歡些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.48,0:07:57.80,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假又是怎樣過的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.88,0:08:03.52,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:10.50,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 我也設成私密賬號就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.72,0:08:12.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,然後讓會長來關注我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.09,0:08:13.75,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你也多少察覺一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.91,0:08:16.88,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,按這個套路可一次都沒成功過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:23.97,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,結果還是沒發申請啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.72,0:08:28.00,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,輝夜大小姐真是頑固得無可救藥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:31.18,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真是一群無可救藥的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:35.33,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只要有一方坦率一點 就能得到幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.88,0:08:38.44,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但我還是好羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.22,0:08:43.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一次也好 我也想像那樣深深喜歡一個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:50.82,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.04,0:08:52.75,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,早坂 趕緊過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.46,0:08:56.34,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,今日戰局 無
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:09:02.93,Kaguya_hm_songti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs80\an8\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\fad(400,0)}因為輝夜與白銀沒有見面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:02.03,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多得了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.98,0:09:05.94,Kaguya_hm_songti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&H010101&\pos(1241.6,472)\fad(230,0)}打\N字\N超\N快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:11.15,Kaguya_hm_title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,400)\bord5\fs83\b1\pos(1322,903.6)}藤原千花超想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.76,0:09:11.59,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,日本~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.27,0:09:14.43,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我好喜歡埃及啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.75,0:09:18.55,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好想再多呆一陣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:22.11,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,炸蠶豆餅和庫沙利都太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.50,0:09:24.72,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是光在惦記著吃的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.18,0:09:26.83,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐你可能是那麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.84,0:09:30.43,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但我可是刻不容緩地想著回日本的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.86,0:09:32.90,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 為啥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.11,0:09:34.38,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:42.49,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫小田島三郎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.69,0:09:44.78,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是個微不足道的中層管理職務
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.83,0:09:47.75,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,興趣是吃遍拉麵店
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:53.70,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.60,0:09:57.20,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,今天來附近的拉麵店
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:10:00.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,點的當然是最受好評的豚骨拉麵…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.14,0:10:02.58,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.76,0:10:04.70,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,而是悄悄被貼在角落裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.94,0:10:08.20,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,醬油豚骨 淡一點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.76,0:10:09.82,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,面要多硬？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.01,0:10:11.20,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,硬一點的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.76,0:10:16.85,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這才是行家才知道的這家店的正確打開方式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.87,0:10:17.49,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.66,0:10:19.99,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,味道真香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.63,0:10:23.04,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀真是位可愛的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.21,0:10:25.60,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,把這當蛋糕店誤入了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.73,0:10:26.60,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要點什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.68,0:10:30.56,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,醬油豚骨 淡一點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:32.29,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.74,0:10:36.77,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼個小姑娘居然找出了這家店的正確打開方式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.08,0:10:39.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是巧合嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.09,0:10:44.85,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不 可是 這店面不像是小女孩會在大半夜來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:49.99,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,難不成這個女人是我們這邊的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:51.29,Kaguya_hm_songti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\bord3\c&H21262C&\3c&H7993A1&\pos(1836.8,222.4)\fad(150,0)}這\N邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:51.29,Kaguya_hm_songti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs120\bord3\c&H232A30&\3c&H7993A1&\b1\pos(1745.6,500.8)\fad(150,0)}會\N吃\N的\N人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.53,0:10:52.75,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,面要多硬？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.45,0:10:55.48,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,特硬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.28,0:10:58.53,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,特硬？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:11:02.03,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,選這種像是玩遊戲用的所謂熱門的硬度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:04.00,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不過是個小丫頭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.04,0:11:05.33,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是多心了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.40,0:11:08.01,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 是我高看她了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:09.84,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.01,0:11:11.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.25,0:11:14.86,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,給小姑娘展示一下正確吃拉麵的方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:17.77,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,首先尋找湯中最本真的香氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.17,0:11:24.31,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,從香氣最濃的紅生薑的對角線開始依次享受才是基本理論
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:28.40,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,當然 店長也熟知這點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:32.87,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟我很中意他把紅生薑放到最遠位置的這份考量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:34.53,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來是味道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.14,0:11:36.97,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,和空氣相混合著品嘗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.57,0:11:42.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,像這樣用上帝視角的方式細細品味嗅覺與味覺傳來的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:47.95,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,然後是面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:50.95,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,先少量地試嚼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:52.65,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,再吞下享受
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.77,0:11:53.40,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:56.86,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.79,0:11:59.47,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,最後是水
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.77,0:12:01.59,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,為了品味到細緻口感的愉悅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.60,0:12:05.25,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,讓殘留在舌頭上的油和鹽味都被水沖走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.13,0:12:08.44,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這步做與不做有著雲泥之別
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.86,0:12:09.97,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,到這 算是一局結束
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:11.56,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,多次重複這個過程
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.57,0:12:13.96,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我們稱這種吃法為「水循環」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.80,0:12:16.51,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 小姐你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.08,0:12:19.66,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,迷你拉麵！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:21.92,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,塞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:22.61,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 果然只是一個普通的小丫頭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:29.24,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,還吃得那麼開心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:32.71,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 也不是這麼做的都是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:35.80,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,一口品嚐到所有美味的迷你拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:39.38,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,也是萬物歸一的究極形態
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.73,0:12:41.50,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這樣一點一點地吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.51,0:12:43.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,面就容易被泡軟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.23,0:12:45.43,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,泡軟…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.26,0:12:48.30,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,特硬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:48.22,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才要了特硬的麵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:51.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這個小丫頭把麵會泡軟也計算上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.56,0:12:56.59,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,而且切得很細的配菜最適合迷你拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.03,0:12:59.69,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能 這些全是她計劃好的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.93,0:13:01.46,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,她應該是東京都內的拉麵四天王
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.15,0:13:03.72,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,神保町的多多媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:05.43,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,巣鴨的仙人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.62,0:13:07.84,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,亦或是高圓寺的J鈴木
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.40,0:13:15.21,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣在拉麵界具有妖精般品味的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:17.52,Kaguya_hm_heiti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord5\b1\fs125\pos(1166.4,422.4)\fad(230,0)}涉 谷 的 小 山
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:19.14,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是還沒完
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.51,0:13:21.39,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,對 還沒完
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.51,0:13:25.24,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,很遺憾 還有一個作為女性無法翻越的壁壘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:26.45,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.29,0:13:28.84,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,大蒜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.17,0:13:30.96,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想從這個味道下逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.01,0:13:33.47,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼很遺憾是假的拉麵控
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.11,0:13:36.20,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,假的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.28,0:13:44.46,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,看來把配菜都吃完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.64,0:13:47.73,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你要怎麼辦 已經沒辦法做迷你拉麵了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.06,0:13:50.28,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.50,0:13:51.41,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.05,0:13:53.34,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要動手嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,0:13:59.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,動手了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:02.45,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙 越過了作為女性的壁壘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:05.63,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話就不能不認同了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:07.00,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,向你致敬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.12,0:14:09.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙是貨真價實的吃貨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.92,0:14:11.70,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是拉麵控！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.91,0:14:19.12,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到 連湯也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.16,0:14:24.72,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,很鹹的 你還放了蒜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.02,0:14:33.24,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我曾經 也有過這樣的時期
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.24,0:14:30.77,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:33.94,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.69,0:14:39.49,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我是怎麼變成大叔的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:44.40,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 跑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:47.45,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我失去的青春的光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.02,0:14:47.86,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,好餓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.52,0:14:54.42,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要堅持到最後啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.53,0:15:03.02,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:05.98,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你等下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.84,0:15:15.63,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,今日的拉麵戰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:17.67,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,藤原勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.94,0:15:20.44,Kaguya_hm_zongyi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\fs93\an8\c&H000000&\pos(1427.2,519.6)\fn华康新综艺W7}你\N{\fnFOT-Comet Std B\fs150}的\N開\N關\N在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.94,0:15:20.44,Kaguya_hm_zongyi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\fs93\an8\c&H000000&\pos(1268.8,691.6)\fn华康新综艺W7}哪\N{\fnFOT-Comet Std B\fs150}裡\N？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:22.35,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,拉麵開關打開了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:27.86,Kaguya_hm_title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,400)\bord5\fs80\b1\pos(1347.2,136)}白銀御行想要遇到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:29.84,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,距離暑假開始已經過了三週
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.71,0:15:33.91,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這期間 什麼都沒有發生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:39.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,只有學習 打工 吃飯 洗澡 睡覺的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.55,0:15:42.43,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,過成最無聊的暑假了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:47.23,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,和輝夜約好的 只有暑假結束的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:48.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,除此之外
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.10,0:15:51.28,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,別說一起出門了 連郵件都沒有發過一封
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.57,0:15:52.76,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,對於他們來說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.87,0:15:57.40,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,邀請對方出去玩這一行為的難度還是很高
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.51,0:16:00.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,明明不該是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:08.17,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宮現在會在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.58,0:16:11.92,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不應該是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.59,0:16:13.95,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.29,0:16:16.30,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這個啊 輝夜大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.50,0:16:19.95,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你把所有的計劃都建立在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.96,0:16:23.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,會長來邀請你的基礎上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:24.43,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.99,0:16:28.75,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你能恬不知恥地隨便翻主人的筆記啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.04,0:16:31.67,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己去約他不就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.78,0:16:33.44,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼蠢話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.51,0:16:36.68,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那不就等於承認我想要和會長出去玩了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.25,0:16:39.80,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是這樣想的吧 我都不知道怎麼反駁好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.23,0:16:45.98,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宮你現在在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:47.61,Kaguya_hm_heiti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H544C4F&\frz333\fs100\an7\pos(536,278)}你要刪除編輯中的郵件嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.61,0:16:48.11,Kaguya_hm_heiti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H544C4F&\frz333\fs100\an7\pos(536,278)}你要刪除編輯中的郵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:48.11,Kaguya_hm_heiti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H544C4F&\frz333\fs80\pos(390.4,604.4)}保存
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:48.11,Kaguya_hm_heiti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H544C4F&\frz333\fs80\pos(926.4,900.8)}刪除
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.04,0:16:52.19,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我是少女嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.23,0:16:54.51,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,寫完了刪寫完了刪的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.76,0:16:56.54,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,初戀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.08,0:16:58.46,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就是初戀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:17:00.18,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不行不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:03.12,Kaguya_zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,快看快看\N活的章魚~~!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:06.75,Kaguya_hm_heiti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H8B8684&\fs60\pos(888,443.2)\frz348.9}剛才電話裡沒說完
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:06.75,Kaguya_hm_heiti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H8B8684&\fs55\an7\frz348.9\pos(658.8,615.2)}今晚好像要降溫\N睡覺時蓋暖和點哦\N晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.65,0:17:11.57,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你再怎麼看郵件也不會增加的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.50,0:17:14.88,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,還設置了郵件保護
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.26,0:17:19.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,會長發的第一封郵件就讓你那麼開心嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:21.91,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,他主動的時候好開心對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.51,0:17:24.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,忘不掉對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.33,0:17:25.64,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.35,0:17:28.24,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我才沒有那樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.68,0:17:31.04,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不要擅自分析別人的內心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.14,0:17:34.10,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我要出門
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.92,0:17:40.29,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,哥 你去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.09,0:17:42.59,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,買晚飯的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.81,0:17:43.95,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,穿校服去？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.26,0:17:46.15,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,順便去一趟學校
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.23,0:17:50.17,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不是順路能到的距離吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.54,0:18:01.18,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我又在做沒意義的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:07.56,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是想到萬一…就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.36,0:18:38.24,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好涼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:47.25,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,想見…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.04,0:19:05.72,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,想想也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.82,0:19:22.65,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假能快點結束就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.01,0:19:26.47,Kaguya_hm_songti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs80\an8\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\fad(400,400)}今日的勝負 無
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.18,0:19:29.73,Kaguya_hm_songti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs80\an8\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\fad(400,400)}因為兩人沒有相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.73,0:19:44.91,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}君と私　きっと今同じ気持ちだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.73,0:19:44.91,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}你和我 現在一定懷著同樣的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.67,0:20:02.01,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}君から笑いかけてくれたなら　天使でいられるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.67,0:20:02.01,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}只要有你的微笑 我就還能如天使一般
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.51,0:20:08.02,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}気付いたの　試されてる　意地悪な駆け引きで
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.51,0:20:08.02,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}已經注意到我在用壞心眼的謀略考驗他了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.27,0:20:11.06,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}後にはもう引けないから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.27,0:20:11.06,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}已經不能退縮了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:13.90,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}仕掛けてあげる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:13.90,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}讓我給你設下圈套吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:21.07,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}さあ　掛かってみせて　戸惑ってみせて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:21.07,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}來吧 掉進陷阱吧 不知所措吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:31.16,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}そして最後に伝えてみせて　好きだって
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:31.16,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}然後在最後說出那句喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.25,0:20:38.84,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}君と私　どんな風に恋するの？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.25,0:20:38.84,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}你和我 將會怎樣相戀呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:42.72,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}探る RELATION
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:42.72,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}去探索 RELATION
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:50.35,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}余裕なんてないよ　見つめられる度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:50.35,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}每次被你注視 我一點都不從容哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.48,0:20:54.15,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}いつも震えてる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.48,0:20:54.15,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}我總是會顫抖著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.27,0:21:01.15,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}素直じゃない私を連れ出して！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.27,0:21:01.15,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}請帶走這樣不坦率的我！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.73,0:21:04.96,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有關於夏天的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.93,0:21:07.91,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你看你看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:11.35,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不過沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.26,0:21:14.68,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有和家人一起去旅行過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.40,0:21:16.68,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.10,0:21:19.92,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,因為每個人都會給我特別的待遇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.14,0:21:23.58,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒去過煙火大會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.60,0:21:25.96,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.52,0:21:30.92,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,因為即使是透過窗子的微弱的光芒我也覺得很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.38,0:21:36.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒和大家一起去購物過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.23,0:21:37.23,Kaguya_hm_heiti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H3B3538&\frz356.9\pos(787.2,219.2)}新郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.23,0:21:37.23,Kaguya_hm_heiti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H3B3538&\an7\fs100\frz357.3\pos(321.6,851.2)}明天在摩艾像前集合~！\N好期待啊~~！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.41,0:21:39.28,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 這個怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.34,0:21:41.24,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,摻雜著不安和期待
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.16,0:21:44.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.79,0:21:46.13,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一起去的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.25,0:21:49.19,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,都是好人 是一群溫柔的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.72,0:21:54.20,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,所以沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.79,0:21:56.41,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.07,0:22:00.69,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我的人生總是不能如願
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.96,0:22:06.89,Kaguya_hm_heiti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H554F50&\fs65\an9}對不起。\N明天不能去購物了。\N\N突然被父親召喚\N所以不得不去京都的本宅。\N\N不用在意我，\N你們玩的開心。\N\N我明天會去煙火大會，\N把今天的事說給我聽吧。\N再見。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.00,0:22:06.71,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,她說「因為突然被父親召喚所以不得不去京都的本宅」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.35,0:22:12.32,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,還說「不用在意我 你們玩的開心」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.02,0:22:13.64,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.32,0:22:16.42,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.06,0:22:18.53,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,決定延期
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.95,0:22:21.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事一定要大家一起去才有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.70,0:22:23.96,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.25,0:22:26.76,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我去和小圭聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.79,0:22:30.92,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我被上天所厚愛著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.70,0:22:34.00,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我有朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.28,0:22:36.57,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,生在令人羨慕的名門
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.90,0:22:39.50,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,還有令人嫉妒的才華
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.32,0:22:44.76,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,有句話說「每個人的幸福與不幸的總和都是一樣的」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.18,0:22:50.09,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,所以被厚愛的我 理應忍受這些
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.27,0:22:55.34,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.97,0:22:59.02,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你在啊 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.78,0:23:08.60,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,把我們叫過來就只有這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.21,0:23:11.02,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,老不死的混蛋老頭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.96,0:23:15.43,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,父親從未和我說過晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.09,0:23:17.11,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,還有一路順風
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.12,0:23:18.03,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.34,0:23:19.78,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸愛你這些
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.78,0:23:21.30,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,都沒有聽到過的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.59,0:23:24.43,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不會傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.08,0:23:27.85,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,從最初就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.08,0:23:30.74,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今也不會有感情波動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.31,0:23:32.25,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.33,0:23:38.42,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,周圍的人們都要求我舉止與家格相稱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.43,0:23:42.96,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,謹小慎微 無可挑剔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.80,0:23:47.56,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就像滲人的日本人偶一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.27,0:23:53.88,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.58,0:23:57.39,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就要去煙火大會了
